      "value": "<p>&gt; @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.nwRAcqBuoleMkfZE]{Weapon Accessories}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListWeaponAccessories_ctl00_LabelName\">Weapons can be fitted with special grips that provide various advantages. You can combine grips by paying the combined price of the grips, but only if all grips are integrated into a weapon. Their benefits stack. The benefits of a grip depend on its type.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListWeaponAccessories_ctl00_LabelName\">A nanofiber grip strengthens your hold on a weapon. While you wield the weapon, microscopic fibers act as setae, clinging to your hands. These fibers grant you a +4 circumstance bonus to AC against disarm combat maneuvers that would disarm you of the weapon.</span></p>"
